creator: SENSOR NOTES
descriptionHtml:
Beat Ball: Dancing Color Hop is most engaging game where you need to clear levels hopping on same colored bricks. Show your hopping skills, concentration power and one finger touch control.
This color jump game is controlled by only one finger or thumb. slide object on screen and make them hop on correct color brick to pass the level.

Features:
- You can play with all your fantastic EDM songs
- Endless Mode
- 100+ levels
- Offline Game
- Endless gameplay
- Free casual arcade game for all ages!
- One finger control.
- Swipe left, right to move your ball.

How to play
- Touch and Drag the ball to make it jump on the Neon Colorfull Tiles.
- Slide the color ball left or right.
- Jump on same color brick.
- Jump at center to collect diamonds.
- Avoid to hop on different colors.
- Don't Miss the right color tiles!
- You can now upload your own songs to play
descriptionShort: Beat Ball: Dancing Color Hop is a dancing ball music game with music EDM rhythm
